reviewText: just what my brother wanted for his birthday its very appreciated thank you so much

The DVD is good quality sound and picture. Interviews!! Not a music DVD!! It is 95 minutes long and consists of 7 interviews in random order from 2009 to 2014. The first 6 interviews are about 6 to 13 minutes each. The last interview is 35 minutes. Very enjoyable and interesting to watch. Shows her intelligence and sense of humor.
